---
// Team Section Component
---

<section class="team-1-section section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="team-1-heading-wrapper">
      <div class="section-title">
        <div class="section-pretitle-box">
          <svg class="pretitle-icon" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><circle cx="9" cy="6" r="3" stroke="#010127" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M3 16c0-3.31 2.69-6 6-6s6 2.69 6 6" stroke="#010127" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
          <span class="pretitle-text">Our team</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Our dedicated team of experts</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-1-section-inner">
      <div class="team-1-grid">
        <div class="team-1-thumbnail">
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6794b96072e9da68ab59307b/67ac94377bd11753a3e0e9bd_img_01.avif" alt="Nina King" class="team-1-image" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="team-1-content">
          <div>
            <div class="team-1-position">UX designer</div>
            <a href="#" class="team-1-item-title">Nina king</a>
            <p class="team-1-desc">Egestas elementum lectus habitant quis lectus turpis sollicitudin vitae blandit. Molestie at quisque arcu pharetra consequat odio non. Mattis id pharetra nisi vitae amet. Commodo ante egestas malesuada pulvinar nec diam vitae.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="team-1-info-block">
              <div class="team-contact-info-wrap">
                <div class="team-contact-info-block">
                  <span class="team-info-title dark-title">Phone number:</span>
                  <a href="tel:+15550123456" class="team-info-desc link dark-text">+1-555-012-3456</a>
                </div>
                <div class="team-contact-info-block">
                  <span class="team-info-title dark-title">Email address:</span>
                  <a href="mailto:nina.king@example.com" class="team-info-desc link dark-text">nina.king@example.com</a>
                </div>
                <div class="team-contact-info-block">
                  <span class="team-info-title dark-title">Location:</span>
                  <span class="team-info-desc dark-text">246 Design St, Moneytown, USA</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="less">
  .team-1-section {
    background-color: var(--color-grey);

    &.section-padding {
      padding-top: 100px;
      padding-bottom: 100px;
    }
  }

  .team-1-section-inner {
    margin-top: 50px;
  }

  .team-1-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
  }

  .team-1-thumbnail {
    border-radius: 15px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .team-1-image {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .team-1-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-flow: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .team-1-position {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    color: var(--color-dark);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .team-1-item-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    color: var(--color-dark);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 42px;
    text-transform: capitalize;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    display: block;

    &:hover {
      color: var(--color-skin-2);
    }
  }

  .team-1-desc {
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .team-info-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    color: var(--color-dark);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 28px;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 150px;
  }

  .team-info-desc {
    color: var(--color-body);
    display: inline-block;

    &.link:hover {
      color: var(--color-skin-2);
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 991px) {
    .team-1-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .team-1-item-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      line-height: 38px;
    }

    .team-1-section.section-padding {
      padding-top: 60px;
      padding-bottom: 60px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 479px) {
    .team-1-item-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      line-height: 38px;
    }
  }
</style>
